<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77254a39-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s281f"><num value="281f">§ 281f.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated the sums of not more than $2,130,000 for the acquisition of lands and interests in land and not more than $9,300,000 for construction, restoration work, and other improvements at the Nez Perce National Historical Park under this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77254a3a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/19/s7">Pub. L. 89–19, § 7</ref>, <date date="1965-05-15">May 15, 1965</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/79/111">79 Stat. 111</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/94/578/tII/s201/10">Pub. L. 94–578, title II, § 201(10)</ref>, <date date="1976-10-21">Oct. 21, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2733">90 Stat. 2733</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/576/s2/7">Pub. L. 102–576, § 2(7)</ref>, <date date="1992-10-30">Oct. 30, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/4771">106 Stat. 4771</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id77254a3b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
